title: image4io - Image Optimization
shortDescription: Optimize your images and make faster websites.
longDescription:
Those images on your website that are taking forever to load?

Yeah, they're causing you to miss out on site visitors and, in turn, money.

Now, if your images are **optimized**, your pages will load faster, **boosting SEO** rankings and **conversion rates**. 

With **[image4io](https://image4.io/en?utm_source=cloudflare&utm_medium=website&utm_campaign=app&utm_term=website)**, you can automatically optimize all the images on your site and get them delivered via image4io's global content delivery network (CDN).

Sign up free [here](https://console.image4.io/Auth/SignUp?utm_source=cloudflare&utm_medium=website&utm_campaign=app&utm_term=website).
instructions: Go to '**[image4io Console](https://console.image4.io?utm_source=cloudflare&utm_medium=website&utm_campaign=app&utm_term=website)**' and get your **cloudname**. Then rename '**src**' attribute in img tag to '**data-src**' on your website. From `` To ``
author: 4AI Information Technologies Inc.
